51\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0628\u064e\u0627\u0631\u064e\u0643\u0650 \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0648\u064e\u0635\u064e\u0641\u064e \u062d\u064f\u0633\u0652\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062e\u064f\u0644\u064f\u0642\u0650 \u0641\u064e\u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0647\u064f\u0648\u064e \u0628\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0637\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0648\u064e\u062c\u0652\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38024,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/07\/26\/sanaiu-al-maroof\/","url_meta":{"origin":17565,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Ma\u2019ruf: Good deeds protect from ruin in the Hereafter","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 26, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cGood works done for people protect those who did them from evil fates, harm, and destruction. The people of goodness in the world will be the people of goodness in the Hereafter.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2165,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/22\/reasons-for-jannah-nar\/","url_meta":{"origin":17565,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Character: Reasons people go to Paradise or Hell","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 22, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, was asked, \u201cWhat admits most people into Paradise?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cFear of Allah and good character.\u201d It was asked, \u201cWhat condemns most people to Hellfire?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThe mouth and the genitals.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24216,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/12\/21\/akhlaq-reward-jannah-adab\/","url_meta":{"origin":17565,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Adab: Good character rewarded with Paradise, increased life","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 21, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, whoever has been given the quality of kindness has been given his share of good in this life and in the Hereafter. Maintaining family ties, good character, and good treatment of neighbors will build their heavenly abodes and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19246,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/05\/28\/long-life-many-hasanat\/","url_meta":{"origin":17565,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Life: Best people have long lives, many good deeds","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 28, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Bakrah reported: A man said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, who are the best people?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cOne whose life is long and his deeds are good.\u201d The man said, \u201cWho are the worst people?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cOne whose life is long\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/17565","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=17565"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/17565\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=17565"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=17565"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=17565"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}